      • shakeScreen

        public void shakeScreen(int verticleAmount,
                        int verticleSpeed,
                        int horizontalAmount,
                        int horizontalSpeed)
        Shakes the player's screen. Parameters 1, 0, 0, 0 to reset.
        Parameters:
        verticleAmount - How far the up and down shaking goes (1-4).
        verticleSpeed - How fast the up and down shaking is.
        horizontalAmount - How far the left-right tilting goes.
        horizontalSpeed - How fast the right-left tiling goes..
